libraries.name: SD
libraries.author: Arduino, SparkFun
libraries.sentence: Enables reading and writing on SD cards.
libraries.paragraph: Once an SD memory card is connected to the SPI interface of the Arduino or Genuino board you can create files and read/write on them. You can also move through directories on the SD card.
